WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:03.101
Počeo bih s pitanjem
za vas, samo podignite ruke:

00:00:03.101 --> 00:00:05.236
Tko ima iPhone?

00:00:05.236 --> 00:00:08.326
Tko ima Android telefon?

00:00:08.330 --> 00:00:10.390
Tko ima Blackberry?

00:00:10.390 --> 00:00:12.768
Tko bi priznao u javnosti da ima Blackberry?

00:00:12.768 --> 00:00:15.351
(Smijeh)

00:00:15.351 --> 00:00:17.439
I dajte da pogodim, koliko vas je,

00:00:17.439 --> 00:00:19.447
po dolasku ovdje, kao i ja, otišlo i kupilo

00:00:19.447 --> 00:00:23.237
SIM karticu na bonove? Da?

00:00:23.237 --> 00:00:24.652
Kladim se da niste znali

00:00:24.652 --> 00:00:26.615
da koristite afričku tehnologiju.

00:00:26.615 --> 00:00:28.898
Kartica na bonove je
tehnologija, odnosno ideja,

00:00:28.898 --> 00:00:31.968
koju je u Africi pokrenula
tvrtka pod imenom Vodacom